===Etymology===
Attested earliest in the ''{{w|Chu Ci}}'' and ''{{w|Guanzi (text)|Guanzi}}'' (translated based on Rickett, 1998):

* {{zh-x|鵾 鴻 群 晨，雜 鶖 鶬 只。||ref=Chuci|collapsed=y}} <!---《大招》--->
* {{zh-x|鵾 鶴 孤 而 夜 號 兮，哀 居 者 之 誠 貞。||ref=Chuci|collapsed=y}} <!---《自悲》--->
* {{zh-x|鵝 鶩 之 舍 近，鵾雞 鵠 䳈{bǎo} 之 通 遠，鵠 鵾 之 所在，君 請 式 璧 而 聘 之。|Resting places for geese and ducks are near by, [...] but '''jungle fowls / cranes''', game cocks, swans, and bustards fly far away. I suggest you used {{w|Nephrite|jade}} ''{{w|Bi (jade)|bi}}'' 璧 to invite peopleliving where there are swans and '''jungle fowls / cranes''' to come to court.|ref=Guanzi|collapsed=yes}} <!---《輕重甲》--->

{{zh-ref|Liu (1999)}} relates it to {{och-l|鯤|mythical large fish}}.

